## 8. 슬래시 커맨드 등록 (신규 방식)

```javascript
SlashCommandParser.addCommandObject(SlashCommand.fromProps({
    name: 'myext',
    callback: (namedArgs, unnamedArgs) => {
        const action = unnamedArgs.toString().trim();
        if (action === 'status') {
            return `Extension is ${getSettings().enabled ? 'ON' : 'OFF'}`;
        }
        return 'Unknown action. Use: /myext status';
    },
    aliases: ['myx'],
    returns: 'Extension status or action result',
    unnamedArgumentList: [
        SlashCommandArgument.fromProps({
            description: 'action to perform',
            typeList: ARGUMENT_TYPE.STRING,
            isRequired: true,
            enumList: ['status', 'toggle'],
        }),
    ],
    helpString: '<div>My Extension command. Usage: <code>/myext status</code></div>',
}));
```

